on\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bbr1665702712405.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bbr1665702712405.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bbr1665702712405.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bbr1665702712405\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Modeled Field Syntax </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__modeled_field_syntax_316863\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for\n      data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control\n      attributes, such dimming and auto-jump. </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96455e1_d96456e1_d96457e1\">For example, a Modeled Field Syntax can define a fixed\n         format for dates, telephone numbers, credit card numbers, or postal codes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96458e1_d96459e1_d96460e1\">Fields that reference the Modeled Field Syntax, inherit\n         the complete field syntax definition. If the Modeled Field Syntax changes, the change is\n         applied to the fields when they are recompiled.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96461e1_d96462e1_d96463e1\">Modeled Field Syntax objects are used during development.\n         They are linked into the component (resolved) during compilation.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__topic_d64512e1_d64513e1_d64514e1_d64515e1_d64516e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d477810e62\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fsy</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bbr1665702712405__table_d10727e1_d10728e1_d10729e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">fsylib:LIB:fsy:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldSyntaxName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__topic_d64517e1_d64518e1_d64519e1_d64520e1_d64521e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d477810e240\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96470e1_d96471e1_d96472e1\">Modeled Field Syntax specializes Development Object in\n            the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39188e1_d39189e1_d39190e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96473e1_d96474e1_d96475e1\">It specifies a value for a <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Field\n                     Syntax</span> property. This is a property of fields that defines some of\n                  the validation rules for data entry, as well as some field display and control\n                  attributes. Other validation rules are determined by the data type, ValRep list,\n                  and validation triggers.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39191e1_d39192e1_d39193e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96476e1_d96477e1_d96478e1\">It has a Modeled Field Syntax Library called\n                     <code class=\"ph codeph\">LIB</code> as parent object.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39194e1_d39195e1_d39196e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96479e1_d96480e1_d96481e1\">It contains no child development objects or code\n                  containers.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39197e1_d39198e1_d39199e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__p_d96482e1_d96483e1_d96484e1\">It has no compiled or generated output.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__topic_d64522e1_d64523e1_d64524e1_d64525e1_d64526e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d477810e282\"> Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39200e1_d39201e1_d39202e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39203e1_d39204e1_d39205e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39206e1_d39207e1_d39208e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vzd1665702584055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vzd1665702584055.html\" title=\"Specify a regex string or a syntax string to define the entry format of the data entered into the field at run time.\">Entry Format</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39209e1_d39210e1_d39211e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iun1665702712476.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iun1665702712476.html\" title=\"Specify whether a user can edit the data in the field. Default is True.\">Edit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39212e1_d39213e1_d39214e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"okr1665702712545.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/okr1665702712545.html\" title=\"Specify whether the data in the field should be displayed. Default is True.\">Display</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39215e1_d39216e1_d39217e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sor1665702604768.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sor1665702604768.html\" title=\"Specify whether the field is included in the prompting sequence. Default is True.\">Prompt</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39218e1_d39219e1_d39220e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aml1665702712619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aml1665702712619.html\" title=\"Specify whether the field is available to the user. Default is False.\">Dimmed</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39221e1_d39222e1_d39223e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wvk1665702676293.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wvk1665702676293.html\" title=\"Specify whether alphanumeric characters in this field are converted to uppercase as the user enters or leaves it.\">Uppercase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39224e1_d39225e1_d39226e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mqc1665702676223.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mqc1665702676223.html\" title=\"Specify whether alphanumeric characters in this field are converted to lowercase as the user enters it or leaves the field.\">Lowercase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39227e1_d39228e1_d39229e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tqh1665702712691.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tqh1665702712691.html\" title=\"Specify whether the field is mandatory.\">Mandatory</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39230e1_d39231e1_d39232e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gkb1665702712761.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gkb1665702712761.html\" title=\"Specify whether data is entered in this field in Overstrike or Insert mode. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Overstrike</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39233e1_d39234e1_d39235e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tsf1665702712830.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tsf1665702712830.html\" title=\"Specify whether the cursor automatically jumps to the next field in the prompt sequence when the maximum field length is reached. The default is False.\">Auto Jump</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39236e1_d39237e1_d39238e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"irh1665702712898.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/irh1665702712898.html\" title=\"Minimum number of characters allowed for data in this field.\">Minimum Field Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39239e1_d39240e1_d39241e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"azy1665702712971.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azy1665702712971.html\" title=\"The maximum number of characters allowed for data in this field.\">Maximum Field Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39242e1_d39243e1_d39244e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fpw1665702713052.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpw1665702713052.html\" title=\"Characters that can be used in the field.\">Characters Allowed</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bbr1665702712405__li_d39245e1_d39246e1_d39247e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"anu1665702713194.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/anu1665702713194.html\" title=\"Use the language-specific input mode in the Input Method Editor.\">Use IME for input</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jjg1714304600909.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Field Syntax Codes</a><p>Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612058\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612058\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Modeled Field Syntax Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Modeled Field Syntax A Modeled Field Syntax is a Development Object that defines some validation rules for data entry in the Field, such as the allowed characters, and field display and control attributes, such dimming and auto-jump. For example, a Modeled Field Syntax can define a fixed format for dates, telephone numbers, credit card numbers, or postal codes. Fields that reference the Modeled Field Syntax, inherit the complete field syntax definition. If the Modeled Field Syntax changes, the change is applied to the fields when they are recompiled. Modeled Field Syntax objects are used during development. They are linked into the component (resolved) during compilation. Characteristics Characteristics Object type code: fsy Main Development Object? No Part of: — Contains: Property Generalization: Development Object Specializations: — Compilation Output: — URI format: fsylib:LIB:fsy: FieldSyntaxName Specialization Modeled Field Syntax specializes Development Object in the following ways: It specifies a value for a Field Syntax property. This is a property of fields that defines some of the validation rules for data entry, as well as some field display and control attributes. Other validation rules are determined by the data type, ValRep list, and validation triggers. It has a Modeled Field Syntax Library called LIB as parent object. It contains no child development objects or code containers. It has no compiled or generated output. Properties Name Description Entry Format Edit Display Prompt Dimmed Uppercase Lowercase Mandatory Overstrike Auto Jump Minimum Field Length Maximum Field Length Characters Allowed Use IME for input Related Links Field Syntax Codes Field syntax codes specify the data entry pattern, the allowed characters, and whether fields are mandatory or read-only. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}